extends baseEmail

block content
    img(src="./public/logo/kanban-logo.png", alt="Kanban Logo")
    p Hi #{firstName},
    p Congratulations! Your password has been successfully set, and your registration is complete. You are now ready to access our platform.  Please click on the button below to login 


    p
        | Thanks,
        br
        |  Kanban team

    table.btn.btn-primary(role='presentation', border='0', cellpadding='0', cellspacing='0')
        tbody
            tr
                td(align='center')
                    table(role='presentation', border='0', cellpadding='0', cellspacing='0')
                        tbody
                            tr
                                td
                                    a(href=`${url}`, target='_blank') log in

    p We look forward to having you on board. If you encounter any issues or have questions, please don't hesitate to reach out to our support team.
    
    p.small
        | This email was sent to 
        span.text-blue #{email}
        | . If you&apos;d rather not receive this kind of email, you can 
        span.text-blue unsubscribe or manage your email preferences
        | .

        p.small Â© 2023 Kanban.

